Virtual environment Setup
==========================
install python3
python3 -m venv cin_env

source cin_env/bin/activate
deactivate

pip install django
Create Djangoproject
====================
django-admin startproject first_project
cd first_project
python manage.py startapp first_app

Run DjangoProject
=================
python manage.py runserver 8080
python manage.py runserver
http://localhost:8000


Django Super user
==================
python manage.py createsuperuser
http://localhost:8000/admin

sqlite3 migrate
===============
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py makemigrations app_name
python manage.py migrate

""" Additional code for ForeignKey"""
topic = models.ForeignKey(
'Topic',
on_delete = models.CASCADE,
)

Support installation setup
==========================
pip install -r requirements.txt


Django flow diagram -----------------------------------------

python manage.py startapp first_app
~add app to settings.py  in installed apps
~add views in app from views.py
~map this view to urls.py (using url mapping of include function)

Add templates 
